img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80aabcace210d8319c29189b0c81ef49e1e856c","tid":1191354,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"近呢幾年黑社會橫行無忌<br />\n日日都有打人劈友 你次次都好似拉唔到人/用極長時間先拉到人<br />\n你呢獲野咁撚快手就做到野 你話唔係做戲真係無人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc67f3f58cc477f89ca2b6527031f4dcc5bd1c3","tid":1191354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}